<br>
I'll leave it to the bards to know which song is the best, but resists and damage shield are the most valuable things a bard can give me as MT. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325267">Brutul Vilesilencer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
