<br>
Psalm of Veeshan on fights where it matters (like stuff procing 3K DDs).<br>
<br>
Rizlona for DPS<br>
<br>
As many DS songs as you can twist.<br>
<br>
Warsong of Zek, Psalm of Veeshan, and Rizlong is a pretty simple combination that does most of what you need.  You can always twist more DS songs of course.<br>
<br>
For xp groups, Rizlona and as many damage songs as you can twist... though usually Rizlona + Warsong of Zek is sufficient.<br>
