<br>
Psalm of Veeshan -- Damage Shield + insane resists<br>
Warsong of Zek -- Damage shield + ATK + haste<br>
Rizlona's Call of Flame -- Haste over the cap + nuke enhancer (if there's damage casters in the group).<br>
<br>
